c: 17
v: 34
t: "wla ttsrrafu fi 'amwal al'atfal aldhyn maat abawhm, wsaru fi kfaltkm, 'iilaa bialtariqat alty hi 'ahsan lhm, wahi altthmyr waltnmyt, hataa yablugh altifl alyatim snn alblwgh, wahusn altasaruf fi almal, wa'atimuu alwafa' bikuli eahid altzmtm bh. 'iina aleahd yas'al allah eanh sahibuh yawm alqyamt, fythybh 'iidha atmh wwffah, wyeaqbh 'iidha khan fyh"